DateTime::Locale::my_MM(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::my_MM(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::my_MM

SYNOPSIS

  use DateTime;

  my $dt = DateTime->now( locale => 'my_MM' );
  print $dt->month_name();

DESCRIPTION

This is the DateTime locale package for Burmese Myanmar [Burma].

DATA

This locale inherits from the DateTime::Locale::my locale.

It contains the following data.
